<a href="http://www.dairyreporter.com/Markets/West-African-consumers-don-t-want-to-walk-10-miles-to-buy-an-ice-cream-Fan-Milk" target="_self">http://www.dairyreporter.com/Markets/West-African-consumers-don-t-want-t...</a></p><p>Danone/Abraaj Group, ‘Danone to join the Abraaj Group in the acquisition of Fan Milk International, a leading dairy products player in West Africa’, 24 October 2013</p><p>
<a href="http://media.corporate-ir.net/media_files/IROL/95/95168/press/24102013_Danone%20Abraaj_-_Fan%20Milk_ENG.pdf" target="_self">http://media.corporate-ir.net/media_files/IROL/95/95168/press/24102013_D...</a></p><p>Reuters, ‘Danone expands footprint in Africa’, 24 October 2013</p><p>
<a href="http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/24/danone-africa-idUSL5N0IE26R20131024" target="_self">http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/24/danone-africa-idUSL5N0IE26R201...</a></p><p>Fan Milk International, ‘History’, web page</p><p>
<a href="http://www.fanmilk.com/index.php?id=70" target="_self">http://www.fanmilk.com/index.php?id=70</a></p><p>Fan Milk International, ‘Business concept’, web page</p><p>
